===============================================================================
OneLoneCode Sprite (SPR) Viewer
===============================================================================

Currently portable. It will open SPR file in current folder. You can also drag
and drop an SPR file into the viewer's window.

KEYS:
=====

PAGE UP     - PREVIOUS FILE
PAGE DOWN   - NEXT FILE
MOUSE DRAG  - MOVE SPRITE
KEYPAD ADD  - ZOOM IN
KEYPAD SUB  - ZOOM OUT
KEYPAD MUL  - RESET ZOOM POS
CURSOR KEYS - PREVIEW SELECT

TAB         - ENTER EDIT MODE
MOUSE LEFT  - PAINT
MOUSE LEFT + CTRL   - GET PIXEL
MOUSE DRAG + SPACE  - MOVE SPRITE
MOUSE DRAG (MIDDLE) - MOVE SPRITE